Add a question here:<br>
<%= form_for @question do |f| %>
  <%= f.label :title %><br>
  <%= f.text_field :title %><br>
  <%= f.label :description %><br>
  <%= f.text_area :description %><br>
  <%= f.submit %>
<% end %><br>


Here is a list of questions and their descriptions that have been asked before:<br>
<ul>
<% @questions.each do |question| %>
  <b>Title:</b><br><%= link_to question.title, question_path(question) %><br>
  <small>Updated at: <%=question.updated_at %></small><br><br>
<% end %>
</ul>

